# 🗂 Internship Application Tracker (Notion Template)

Here’s a Notion template I use to track my tech internship applications. You can duplicate it and use it for your own job hunt:

🔗 [Use the template here](https://sheer-lobster-282.notion.site/Internship-application-tracker-1e53c77369b380a58bafe37532dd47a1?pvs=4)

--
💡 To use the template, click the link above and duplicate it into your own Notion workspace.

## What It Includes
- Deadline tracking
- Each entry opens as a page to prepare “Why this company” answers  
- Clean, checkbox-based workflow for managing application progress
- Customisable filters/views
